# Description: This OPTIONAL file is a configuration module
# for "sudo" and it contains definition of some command lines
# needed for (CI-driven or manual) testing of the $BIOS project.
# It relies on values set in the bios_sudo_conf_00_base file.
# See also the script to generate these needed $BIOS accounts:
#    tools/init-os-accounts.sh
#
